import React from 'react'
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom'
import './index.css'
import App from './App'
import reportWebVitals from './reportWebVitals'
import { Web3Provider } from 'react-web3'

ReactDOM.render(
	<Web3Provider>
		<React.StrictMode>
			<App />
		</React.StrictMode>
		, document.getElementById('root')
	</Web3Provider>
)

reportWebVitals()
